Revision history for Perl extension Win32::ActAcc.

0.1  August 12, 2000
	- original version

0.2  September 16, 2000
	- installable by PPM

0.5  March 11, 2001
	- waitForEvent returns whatever your code-reference returns
	- Desktop() function
	- Bundle PPM package for ActivePerl
	- Sample: answer incoming AOL Instant Messages using Chatbot::Eliza 

1.0  August 12, 2001
	- Iterators
	- conveniences for operating tree-views and menus